704675f-a.text:
Graham Ave., east side, north of Jackson to Frost Streets. Intersecting the center of the view is Withers Street. The building at the extreme right foreground is No. 400. The Synagogue was once the German Evang.
Reformed Church.
March 3, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
